<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(انْهَكُوا الشَّوَارِبَ، وَأَعْفُوا اللِّحَى)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
